            <title><![CDATA[歼-16D、无侦-7将首次亮相中国航展]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-09/4bbd-fe0590ac904bb70eddf68d404e434e0b.jpg?j9DNrxg1MprfnVCtZX47AROuWJB.OMUA&h=5ed65e0b&itok=8_8leSxr" title="歼-16D战斗机将在中国航展首次亮相。（央视军事）" alt="歼-16D战斗机将在中国航展首次亮相。（央视军事）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-09/4bbd-fe0590ac904bb70eddf68d404e434e0b.jpg?j9DNrxg1MprfnVCtZX47AROuWJB.OMUA&h=5ed65e0b&itok=8_8leSxr" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
